aste would give you 0 dly and you would swing and infinite amount of times per second.<br>
<br>
<br>
40% haste means you get 40% more attacks.  If you have spell haste and item haste it adds the 2 then figures out your dly.<br>
<br>
100(unhasted dly) / new haste percentage +100 = new dly<br>
<br>
For ragebringer haste its 100 / (40 +100) = .71<br>
<br>
7.1 seconds for bs in other words.<br>
<br>
.5 = 50% of original dly<br>
.6 = 60% of original dly<br>
<br>
and so on<br>
<br>
Epic haste + 49 enc haste = 100% haste so its...<br>
<br>
100 / (100+100) = .5<br>
<br>
5 seconds for bs refresh in other words.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
